The 14-year-old girl charged with allegedly assaulting Lufuno Mavhunga has been granted bail. A video of her assaulting Lufuno went viral and is believed to have led to the teenager taking her life. #eNCA​ Courtesy #DStv403 THOHOYANDOU - The 14-year-old girl charged with allegedly assaulting Lufuno Mavhunga has been granted bail. A video of her assaulting Lufuno went viral and is believed to have led to take her life. READ: Family wants justice for Lufuno Mavhunga The teenager was granted R1,500 bail at the Thohoyandou Magistrate's Court. Watch the video above for details on this story